---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TrustedBy from '../components/TrustedBy.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Catering Vancouver | Indian Catering for Weddings & Corporate Events"
	description="Indian catering Vancouver for weddings, corporate events, and private parties. Halal, vegan, vegetarian options. Award-winning since 2010. From $21.95 per person."
	canonical="/catering-vancouver"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org","@type": "Service",
			"name": "Catering Vancouver",
			"provider": {"@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization"},
			"areaServed": {"@type": "City", "name": "Vancouver"},
			"serviceType": "Indian Catering"
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('/uploads/vancouver-catering-weddings.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>Catering<br/>in <em>Vancouver</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">Award-winning Indian catering across downtown Vancouver, the West End, East Van, and beyond. Fifteen years, 2,000+ events.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/request-a-quote/" class="btn btn-gold">Request Vancouver Catering</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TrustedBy />


	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<h2>Indian Catering Across <em>Vancouver</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
				<p>Vancouver is home. We've operated here since 2010, three full-service restaurants on Commercial Drive, Davie Street, and Main Street, plus our newest addition, Sula Café in East Van. <a href="/" class="body-link">Sula Catering</a> brings that same hospitality to events across every neighbourhood. From downtown corporate boardrooms to West End wedding venues, North Van celebrations to East Van warehouse parties, we cater all of Vancouver.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="/uploads/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond-office.webp" alt="Indian food catering Vancouver" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">What We Cater in Vancouver</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Every <em>Occasion</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="service-grid-v2">
				<a href="/weddings" class="service-card-v2 reveal">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-wedding-catering.webp" alt="Wedding catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Vancouver Weddings</span>
							<h3>Wedding <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>South Asian weddings across Vancouver, sangeet, ceremony, reception. Halal, vegetarian, vegan, Jain.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Weddings →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/corporate" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-100">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/office-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Corporate catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Vancouver Offices</span>
							<h3>Corporate <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Office lunches, conferences, client entertaining. From Yaletown towers to Mount Pleasant studios.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Corporate →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/private-parties" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-200">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/private-party-vancouver-catering.webp" alt="Private party Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Vancouver Celebrations</span>
							<h3>Private <em>Parties</em></h3>
							<p>Birthdays, anniversaries, housewarmings, Diwali. From West End condos to East Van homes.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Private →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-300">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Cafe catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">From East Van</span>
							<h3>Café <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Live chai, specialty coffee, fresh pastries, directly from Sula Café in East Van.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Café →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-plum pattern-mandala">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="experience">
				<div class="experience-img reveal-left">
					<img src="/uploads/wedding-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Vancouver catering" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="experience-content reveal-right">
					<h2>We Know <em>Vancouver</em></h2>
					<p>Our four locations span the city. Commercial Drive sits at the heart of East Van. Davie Street anchors the West End. Main Street covers Mount Pleasant and Riley Park. Sula Café serves the False Creek Flats.</p>
					<p>That local knowledge translates into catering. We know which venues need staff parking. We know the loading docks. We know which neighbourhoods need extra time for delivery on weekday mornings. We also cater across <a href="/catering-burnaby" class="body-link">Burnaby</a>, <a href="/catering-richmond" class="body-link">Richmond</a>, and <a href="/catering-surrey" class="body-link">Surrey</a>.</p>
					<div class="experience-stats">
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">4</div><div class="stat-label">Locations</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">15+</div><div class="stat-label">Years</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">$5</div><div class="stat-label">Flat Delivery</div></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Common Questions</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Vancouver Catering <em>FAQs</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="faq-list">
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you deliver catering across Vancouver?</h3><p>Yes, across all neighbourhoods, including downtown, West End, East Van, Mount Pleasant, Kitsilano, and the West Side. $5 flat delivery, no minimum order.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>How fast can you deliver in Vancouver?</h3><p>Standard catering needs 48 hours notice. Same-day or last-minute catering may be available depending on guest count.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you cater downtown Vancouver high-rises?</h3><p>Often. Our team handles loading dock coordination and freight elevator timing for downtown corporate buildings.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>What's the minimum order for Vancouver delivery?</h3><p>No minimum. We've delivered catering for groups of 8 and 800.</p></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>


	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<h2>Catering for <em>Vancouver</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us your neighbourhood, your guest count, your dates.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/request-a-quote/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
